ABOUT THIS GAME:

This is a comprehensive backgammon game with a choice of
challenging computer opponents. Extensive choice of rules
includes domino backgammon: a new variation that replaces the
dice with dominoes and allows players to think ahead instead of
relying on the roll of the dice. Now includes seven extra
backgammon variations and four backgammon challenges: series of
matches against progressively improving computer opponents.
